# aabd2c6dae334424b0e3eefdf8ee9adf
msgid "InaSAFE provides overviews of potential disaster scenarios, of their outcomes, as well as maps which can aid decision makers when disaster strikes.  Maps are an effective way of communicating disaster impact, but showing in a simple way the areas of damage, such as the extent of flood-affected areas and buildings affected by a flood."
